data.meta_description:
169 likes, 112 comments - davidyontef on May 18, 2024: "New Episode Alert 🚨!
Another week, another episode of RHONJ.  We break down this week’s episode with the help of the one and only Tre, as played by Andrea Lopez. Next, we cover all that has been going on in the real world summarizing the many interviews the cast has been doing, less Jennifer Aydin who is rumored to have been banned from interviews due to allegedly leaking Season 14 screeners.  Teresa says her parents support her not speaking to Joe, Joey claps back, Melissa reminds Bravo who the “dream team” is, Teresa denies she pays fan Podcasts, Marge and Mel are outraged at Tre’s behavior, Jackie says the toxic franchise has become “The Hunger Games” and the entire cast, viewers and us all agree that none of this weekly vitriol is sustainable.  Whew, and we are only two episodes in. @andrealopezcomedy @behindvelvetrope @davidyontef #rhonj #TeresaGiudice #melissagorga #margaretjosephs #jackiegoldschneider #jenfessler #jenniferaydin #daniellecabral #rachelfuda #dolorescatania 💣💣🧨🧨🥊🥊💥💥🔥🔥🚨🚨🙏🙏".
